<hymn_number>6498</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ʿndmạ kẖlṣt nfsy mn hlạk ạ̉bdy
 fy ạlsmạ tẖbt gẖrsy bḥnạn ạ̉bwy
 lm tkn fḍlẗ rḥmẗ lst tḥtạj ạ̹lyhạ
 lm tkn ạ̉rkẖṣ nʿmẗ ḥṣl ạlnạs ʿlyhạ
 flqd ạ̉ʿṭyt ḥty̱ lm yʿd bʿd mzyd
 fạlʿṭạyạ hy ạ̉nt mạ ạldẖy bʿd ạ̉ryd
 mt ạ̹dẖ ʿạdlt ʿmraⁿạ wḥyạẗ bḥyạẗ
 fjʿlt ạljsm jsraⁿạ mʿbraⁿạ lllsmwạt
 tẖmn ạlạ̹nqạdẖ gẖạl wạltkạlyf kbyrẗ
 kṣlyb ạlḥb ʿạl ymlạ̉ ạlạ̉nfs ḥyrẗ</lyrics>
<title>ʿndmạ kẖlṣt</title>
</song>